 "Title":"Relates to audio-visual coverage of judicial proceedings by the media; repealer",
 "Summary":"Relates to audio-visual coverage of judicial proceedings by the media; allows the judge or justice presiding over a proceeding to exercise discretion to prohibit or limit filming or photographing of particular participants; defines terms; provides limitations on audio-visual coverage.",
